title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E08 720p [TankEngine]
description:
Sure, it already aired in China, France and now Portugal, but here's Transformers RID 2015 S01E08 in English! This is the first and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but remember to give credit where credit is due.

Chapter markings are included for your convenience.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back tomorrow for episode 9, with more to come in the future!

N.B.:

A certain Network that happens to air Cartoons managed to ruin the closing credits again, so I sourced a replacement (again). Therefore, the Chinese credits were used (which are, as you may already know, still in complete English). The only difference is, of course, the watermarks
